Excellent yong tau hu: approved by wife!

They will take the effort to heat up the fried yong tau hu for you, so they would be hot and crispy as you bite into them.

The ingredients are fresh, essential for a good bow of yong tau hu.
Dishonest pricing policies and lack of communication. If I can give Zero Stars, I would.
